    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6592787>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Arcotheres tivelae (Gordon, 1936). A–C, holotype female (13.6 × 11.5 mm) (NHM 1936.6.19.9), Muscat; D–F, G, I, A–D, F, female (11.2 × 9.8 mm) (ZRC 2009.0831), Iran; H, female (10.1 × 9.1 mm) (ZRC 2016.162), Iran. A, D, overall dorsal view; B, E, frontal view of cephalothorax; C, F, ventral view of cephalothorax; G, right third maxilliped; H, right chela; I, right P5 (ventral view). Scales: 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6592787/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6592789>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Arcotheres tivelae (Gordon, 1936), female (11.2 × 9.8 mm) (ZRC 2009.0831), Iran.A, right MXP3 (denuded); B–E, right P2–P5, respectively; F–I, left P2–P5, respectively. Scales: A = 0.5 mm; B–I = 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6592789/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6592791>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Arcotheres tivelae (Gordon, 1936), male (5.7 × 5.6 mm) (ZRC 2011.0155), Iran. A, overall dorsal view; B, dorsal view of carapace; C, left third maxilliped; D, frontal view of cephalothorax; E, pleon; F, left chela; G, left P5 (ventral view); H, right G1 (ventral view); I, right G1 (dorsal view)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6592791/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6592793>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Arcotheres tivelae (Gordon, 1936), male (5.7 × 5.6 mm) (ZRC 2011.0155), Iran.A, left MXP3 (denuded); B–E, left P2–P5, respectively; F, right G1 (ventral view); G, right G1 (dorsal view); H, distal part of right G1 (denuded, ventral view); I, distal part of right G1 (denuded, dorsal view); J, left G2. Scales: A, F, G, J = 0.2 mm; B–E = 0.5 mm; H, I = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6592793/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6592797>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Colour in life. Arcotheres tivelae (Gordon, 1936).A, host clam, Callista umbonella; B, female (part of ZUTC 6924); C, D, female (8.4 × 7.7 mm) (ZUTC 6923). B, in situ in Callista umbonella; C, overall dorsal view; D, overall ventral view. All from Iran." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6592797/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

